data.description: Prime Location! Don't miss this incredible chance to own a condominium that's conveniently situated near Town Center, military bases, major highways, shopping centers, restaurants, and much more. This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom condo boasts 1,650 square feet of living space, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, elegant laminate flooring, and the added convenience of an attached garage. The community itself offers a wealth of outstanding amenities, including scenic walking paths, playgrounds, a clubhouse, a dog park, and a refreshing pool for your enjoyment.
